    "The LLM finds information that Donald Trump did a lap around the race but correctly concludes that no information indicates that he did \"burnouts.\"",
    "The full examples, including all Google results, are shown in the Supplementary material.",
    "Examples of PolitiFact statements for which the model returns incorrect responses.",
    "We show the Google queries performed by the LLM and the first results of each query.",
    "The LLM is asked to verify whether the Obama administration paid a ransom payment to Iran."
